Class FoodTruck

java.lang.Object
KI304.Moh.Lab6.FoodTruck
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Vehicle>, Vehicle
public class FoodTruck extends Object implements Vehicle
The FoodTruck class represents a specialized type of vehicle designed for transporting food. It implements the Vehicle interface and provides information about its carrying capacity and temperature mode.
